# =============================================================================
# Branch: develop — track everything needed to MAINTAIN and refresh skills:
#   - .cursor/skills/           (skills + packaged indexes shipped to users)
#   - scripts/                  (build-api-index.ps1, build-index.ps1, helpers)
#   - existingCodes/            (source corpus for scaffolding samples-index)
#   - setup.ps1                 (verify / regenerate packaged outputs)
#   plus README.md and this file.
#
# Still excluded: RevitAPI.chm (Autodesk redistribution), transient API index
# rebuild artifacts (bak/new/rename-stage), and decompressed CHM HTML under
# docs/html/ — regenerate locally; see README.md.
# =============================================================================

*

!.gitignore
!README.md
!setup.ps1

!scripts/
!scripts/**/*

!existingCodes/
!existingCodes/**/*

!.cursor/
!.cursor/**/*

# --- revit-api-lookup: do not commit CHM; packaged JSONL + md sidecars yes
.cursor/skills/revit-api-lookup/*.chm

.cursor/skills/revit-api-lookup/docs/*

!.cursor/skills/revit-api-lookup/docs/
!.cursor/skills/revit-api-lookup/docs/symbols.jsonl
!.cursor/skills/revit-api-lookup/docs/md/
!.cursor/skills/revit-api-lookup/docs/md/**

.cursor/skills/revit-api-lookup/docs/symbols.jsonl.bak.*
.cursor/skills/revit-api-lookup/docs/symbols.jsonl.new
.cursor/skills/revit-api-lookup/docs/md/.rename-stage-*/

# --- Build / IDE noise (often present under existingCodes sample solutions)
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/packages/
**/TestResults/
**/*.csproj.user
**/*.vbproj.user
**/*.props.user
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
**/.vs/
# Local experiment outputs outside tracked roots (if any)
sandbox/
scratch-addins/
local-addins/
generated-addins/
